ed: People from virus-hit city tracked, quarantined |first=Dake |last=Kang |date=31 January 2020 |agency=Associated Press}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"bZ2hk\">{{cite web |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/\u6b66\u6c49\u80ba\u708e\u75c5\u6bd2\u6301\u7eed\u6269\u6563-\u6e56\u5317\u4e0b\u4ee4\u5c0115\u4e2a\u57ce\u5e02/a-52132769 |date=24 January 2020 |publisher=Deutsche Welle |location=Germany |language=zh-hans |script-title=zh:\u6b66\u6c49\u80ba\u708e\u75c5\u6bd2\u6301\u7eed\u6269\u6563 \u6e56\u5317\u4e0b\u4ee4\u5c0115\u4e2a\u57ce\u5e02 |url-status=live |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200124234427/https://www.dw.com/zh/\u6b66\u6c49\u80ba\u708e\u75c5\u6bd2\u6301\u7eed\u6269\u6563-\u6e56\u5317\u4e0b\u4ee4\u5c0115\u4e2a\u57ce\u5e02/a-52132769 |archive-date=24 January 2020 |access-date=25 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"0JDLl\">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-51813876 |title=Coronavirus: China says disease 'curbed' in Wuhan and Hubei |date=10 March 2020 |work=BBC}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"6nex7\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/15/business/china-coronavirus-lockdown.html |title=To Tame Coronavirus, Mao-Style Social Control Blankets China |date=18 February 2020 |work=[[The New York Times]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"eFQeZ\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-51906693 |script-title=zh:\u80ba\u708e\u75ab\u60c5\uff1a\u4e2d\u56fd\u52a0\u5f3a\u5165\u5883\u7ba1\u63a7\uff0c\u5927\u6279\u7559\u5b66\u751f\"\u7ec4\u56e2\"\u56de\u56fd |date=17 March 2020 |work=BBC News|access-date=17 March 2020 |language=zh}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"mey8S\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/29/opinion/coronavirus-china-government.html |title=Coronavirus Spreads, and the World Pays for China's Dictatorship |last1=Kristof |first1=Nicholas |date=29 January 2020 |work=[[The New York Times]] |access-date=2 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"siStf\">{{cite news |title='Hero who told the truth': Chinese rage over coronavirus de